    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it does show signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the driver's side rear panel, and some fading of the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear, and all major electronics are functional, though the air conditioning takes a moment to cool down. It has been regularly serviced, though it will likely need new tires and a brake pad replacement in the near future.",
      "price": 19000.0,
